Description.Text: The hotel offers guests access to a variety of water sports, there is also a health centre. And a golf course is just a few minutes away.
The hotel is located near Cancun's convention centre, shopping malls and restaurants, in the Kukulcan Avenue.

The rooms are large in size and are decorated with Mexican furniture and pastel colours, all with modern facilities and in very good conditions. All rooms have a large bathroom in very good conditions.
The hotel has two restaurants serving Mediterranean, International and local cuisine. Both of them at pool level.

The lobby is large in size with a large seating area. Next to the reception is as ramp which descend to the lower ground of pool level where you can find the lobby bar, hotel shops and access to the hotel main restaurant.
